"Markdown.\nThe game begins as the player awakens from a strange sleep, the effects of which are still unknown. Throughout the game, the player will embark on an adventure alongside companions they meet along the way. The journey will pit them against strange and dangerous creatures. In the end, the player must make a choice that will either lead to their freedom or ultimate peril.\nThe synopsis consists of the player joining forces with their companions in the fight against the unknown forces. Together, the group fights the dangerous creatures to regain control over the world, only to find out they were the ones who created the problem in the first place. Finally, the player must face off against their friends to decide their fate or seek an honorable way out to the end."